* Task 5 fixture: PERFORM with both inline definition and external reference
* This program defines an inline subroutine SHARED-LOGIC (DEFINE SUBROUTINE).
* It performs both the inline SHARED-LOGIC and an EXTERNAL-ONLY (not defined).
* Accepts the Task 5 criterion: inline subroutine targets are marked in-file-resolved;
* external-only targets are left unresolved (deferred to resolution feature).

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 STATUS-CODE (N2)
END DEFINE

PERFORM SHARED-LOGIC

MOVE 1 TO STATUS-CODE

PERFORM EXTERNAL-ONLY

WRITE 'Done'

DEFINE SUBROUTINE SHARED-LOGIC
  WRITE 'Shared logic'
END-SUBROUTINE

END
